data.description: OPEN HOUSE FOR 12/16 is CANCELLED. Welcome to 4341 Deerpath Lane! This 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home boasts 1,260 square feet of living space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by hardwood floors and large windows including the large bay window allowing for tons of natural light. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, black subway tile backsplash, and tons of white cabinetry for storage. Then step outside to the back patio, where you can enjoy a peaceful moment or fire up the grill for some outdoor dining. Upstairs, you’ll find 3 generous-sized bedrooms offering ample closet space. This home has a spacious basement, perfect for a secondary living area, home office, home gym & so much more. In close proximity to all of the restaurants, bars, grocery stores, parks, and coffee shops that Torresdale has to offer, this home is in a perfect location. Schedule your showing today!
